Program: Discovery
Title: Water - the giver of life
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrycq
Last Broadcast Date: 23 April 2003
Voyage through the science of water and following the H2O around our planetary system. Life on earth would not have started without water. There is also a lot of water in our solar system in all its different forms, ice, vapour and in its liquid form, which is necessary for life. Picture: Water and oil, Credit: Thinkstock Show less